SELECT 
  FP."SRC_ACTIVITY_ID", 
  FP."SRC_DELETED_FLG" 
FROM ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_env_AAW_EDW_Schema}."FACT_PRODUCER" FP
WHERE SRC_TABLE_NAME = 'SFDC.EVENT'

SELECT 
E.JB_SOURCE_NAME__C AS JOB_SOURCE_NAME,
E.JOB_POSTING_OWNER_EMAIL__C AS JOB_POSTING_OWNER_EMAIL,
E.SOURCE__C AS EVENT_SOURCE,
E.JB_SOURCE_ID__C AS JOB_SOURCE_ID,
E.VENDOR_APPLICATION_ID__C AS VENDOR_APPLICATION_ID,
E.ID AS EVENT_ID,
E.FEED_SOURCE_ID__C FEED_SOURCE_ID,
E.VENDOR_SEGMENT_ID__C AS EVENT_VENDOR_SEGMENT_ID,
APP.ROI_VENDOR_NAME__C AS VENDOR_ROI_NAME
FROM ${v_env_Data_Lake_DB}.${v_env_SFDC_Schema}.EVENT E
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_Data_Lake_DB}.${v_env_SFDC_Schema}.APPLICATION_SOURCE__C APP ON E.JB_SOURCE_ID__C=APP.SOURCE_ID__C

select 
DJP.JOB_POSTING_GK,
DJP.SRC_POSTING_ID,
DJP.REQ_GK,
DJP.OWNER_PERSON_GK,
DJP.POSTING_DISTRIBUTION_DATE,
DJP.POSTING_NAME,
DJP.JOB_TITLE,
DJP.CREATED_DATE,
DJP.EXPIRATION_DATE,
DJP.BROADBEAN_ACCOUNT_ID,
DJP.CITY_NAME,
DJP.STATE_NAME,
DJP.COUNTRY_NAME,
DR.REQ_ID,
DR.ACCOUNT_GK,
DR.DIVISION_ID,
DR.JOB_CODE_ID,
DR.DIVISION_NAME,
DR.BRAND_CODE AS DIM_REQ_BRAND_CODE,
DREQ_BRANDNAME.BRAND_NAME AS DIM_REQ_BRAND_NAME,
DR.REQ_NEXTGEN_DIVISION,
DR.REQ_FUNCTIONAL_IND,
DR.REQ_SKILL_SPECIALTY,
DR.REQ_SKILL, 
DP.PERSON_ID,
DP.FULL_NAME,
DP.ROLE_PRIMARY,
DP.OFFICE_ID,
DP.OFFICE_NAME,
DP.BRAND_CODE AS DIM_PERSON_BRAND_CODE,
DPERS_BRANDNAME.BRAND_NAME AS DIM_PERSON_BRAND_NAME,
DR.JOB_CODE_NAME,
DR.OPERATING_COMPANY,
DR.REQ_CREATED_DATE,
DR.REQ_CLOSE_DATE,
DR.REQ_TOP_SKILLS,
DR.REQ_REST_OF_SKILLS,
JP.INDUSTRY_SECTOR__C AS INDUSTRY_SECTOR,
JP.JOB_CATEGORY__C AS JOB_CATEGORY,
JP.POSTING_STATUS__C AS POSTING_STATUS,
JP.OPCO__C AS JP_OPCO,
JP.OFFICE__C AS JP_OFFICE,
JP.ISDELETED AS JP_DELETED_FLG,
DA.ACCOUNT_LEGAL_NAME,
USR.DIVISION__C AS USER_DIVISION_NAME,
USR.OFFICE_CODE__C AS OFFICE_CODE,
USR.PEOPLESOFT_ID__C AS POSTING_CREATOR,
USR.OPCO__c AS USER_OPCO,
DP2.FULL_NAME AS OPPORTUNITY_OWNER,
DR.DELETED_FLG AS DR_DELETED_FLG,
-- Below cols added as a part of story (S-430703)
DR.OFFICE_ID AS REQ_OFFICE_ID,
DR.OFFICE_NAME AS REQ_OFFICE_NAME,
DP2.DIVISION_ID AS REQ_OWNER_DIVISION_ID,
DP2.DIVISION_NAME AS REQ_OWNER_DIVISION_NAME,
DP2.OFFICE_ID AS REQ_OWNER_OFFICE_ID,
DP2.OFFICE_NAME AS REQ_OWNER_OFFICE_NAME,
DP2.OPERATING_COMPANY REQ_OWNER_OPERATING_COMPANY,
DP.OPERATING_COMPANY AS POSTING_OWNER_OPERATING_COMPANY
FROM ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_job_Target_Schema}.DIM_JOB_POSTING DJP
LEFT JOIN ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_job_Target_Schema}.DIM_REQ DR ON DJP.REQ_GK = DR.REQ_GK
LEFT JOIN ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_job_Target_Schema}.DIM_PERSON DP ON DJP.OWNER_PERSON_GK = DP.PERSON_GK
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_job_Target_Schema}.DIM_BRAND DREQ_BRANDNAME ON DREQ_BRANDNAME.BRAND_CODE=DR.BRAND_CODE
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_job_Target_Schema}.DIM_BRAND DPERS_BRANDNAME ON DPERS_BRANDNAME.BRAND_CODE=DP.BRAND_CODE
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_Data_Lake_DB}.${v_env_SFDC_Schema}.JOB_POSTING__C JP ON  DJP.SRC_POSTING_ID = JP.id
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_Data_Lake_DB}.${v_env_SFDC_Schema}.USER USR ON  JP.CREATEDBYID = USR.ID
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_job_Target_Schema}.DIM_ACCOUNT DA ON  DR.ACCOUNT_GK=DA.ACCOUNT_GK
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_job_Target_Schema}.DIM_PERSON DP2 ON DR.PRIMARY_OWNER_ID=DP2.PERSON_ID AND DP2.SRC_SYSTEM_NAME IN ('PS','SFDC','HUB','NA')

SELECT
O.ID as ORDERID,
NVL(O.START_FORM_ID__C,E.NAME) AS ESF_ID,
O.STATUS AS ORDER_STATUS,
OPP.REQ_DIVISION__C AS REQ_DIVISION,
OPP.NAME AS  REQ_NAME,
OPP.STAGENAME AS STAGE_NAME,
OPP.LDS_STATUS__C AS LDS_STATUS,
OPP.REQ_TOTAL_POSITIONS__C AS  REQ_TOTAL_POSITIONS,
OPP.REQ_JOB_TITLE__C AS REQ_JOB_TITLE,
OPP.REQ_GRADE__C AS REQ_GRADE,
OPP.REQ_TEAM_VALUE__C AS REQ_TEAM_VALUE,
OPP.OPPORTUNITY_NUM__C AS OPPORTUNITY_NUM,
OPP.OPCO__C AS REQ_OPCO_DESC,
PR.JOBCODE_ID__C JOB_CODE_ID
FROM ${v_env_Data_Lake_DB}.${v_env_SFDC_Schema}."ORDER" O
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_Data_Lake_DB}.${v_env_SFDC_Schema}.OPPORTUNITY OPP ON  O.OPPORTUNITYID = OPP.ID
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_Data_Lake_DB}.${v_env_SFDC_Schema}.PRODUCT2 PR ON OPP.LEGACY_PRODUCT__C=PR.ID
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_Data_Lake_DB}.${v_env_SFDC_Schema}.EMPLOYEE_STATUS_FORM__C E ON (O.EMPLOYEE_STATUS_FORM__C=E.ID)

SELECT 
DP.PERSON_ID,
DP.FULL_NAME,
DP.PERSON_GK,
CON.Peoplesoft_id__C AS SRC_EMPLOYEE_ID,
CON.createdDate AS CANDIDATE_CREATED_DATE,
CON.email AS HOME_EMAIL,
CON.Other_Email__C AS OTHER_EMAIL,
CON.Work_Email__C AS WORK_EMAIL,
CON.HomePhone AS HOME_PHONE,
CON.OtherPhone AS OTHER_PHONE,
CON.Phone AS WORK_PHONE,
CON.SOURCE_SYSTEM_ID__C AS SRC_CANDIDATE_ID,
CON.MobilePHone AS MOBILE_PHONE,
CON.LASTMODIFIEDDATE AS CONTACT_LAST_MOD_DDTM, 
CON.MAILINGCITY AS MAILING_CITY,
CON.MAILINGSTATE AS MAILING_STATE,
CON.MAILINGCOUNTRY AS MAILING_COUNTRY,
CON.MAILINGPOSTALCODE AS MAILING_POSTAL_CODE,
CON.LAST_ACTIVITY_DATE__C AS LAST_ACTIVITY_DATE,
CON.TALENT_ID__C AS NEW_CANDIDATE_ID,
ACC.ID AS ACCOUNT_ID,
ACC.CANDIDATE_STATUS__C AS CANDIDATE_STATUS
FROM ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_job_Target_Schema}.DIM_PERSON DP
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_Data_Lake_DB}.${v_env_SFDC_Schema}.CONTACT CON ON DP.PERSON_ID = CON.id AND DP.SRC_SYSTEM_NAME IN ('PS','SFDC','HUB','NA')
LEFT OUTER JOIN ${v_env_Data_Lake_DB}.${v_env_SFDC_Schema}.ACCOUNT ACC ON ACC.id = CON.accountid

SELECT * FROM
(
  SELECT *, ROW_NUMBER() OVER (PARTITION BY FACT_APPLICATION_GK ORDER BY ACTIVITY_DATE)RN FROM
  (
    (
      SELECT 
      FACT_APPLICATION.FACT_APPLICATION_GK,
      FACT_APPLICATION.SRC_APPLICATION_ID,
      FACT_APPLICATION.JOB_POSTING_GK,
      FACT_APPLICATION.APPLICANT_PERSON_GK,
      FACT_APPLICATION.VENDOR_SEGMENT_GK,
      FACT_APPLICATION.TALENT_VENDOR_GK,
      FACT_APPLICATION.DATE_APPLIED,
      FACT_APPLICATION.EXTERNAL_CAMPAIGN_ID,
      FACT_APPLICATION.INTERNAL_CAMPAIGN_ID,
      FACT_APPLICATION.ADOBE_CLOUD_VISITOR_ID,
      FACT_APPLICATION.SRC_ORDER_ID,
      FACT_APPLICATION.HAS_APPLICATION_FLG,
      FACT_APPLICATION.MATCH_SCORE,
      FACT_APPLICATION.EVENT_TYPE,
      FACT_APPLICATION.JOB_SOURCE_NAME,
      FACT_APPLICATION.JOB_SOURCE_ID,
      FACT_APPLICATION.APPLICATION_DATE
      FROM ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_job_Target_Schema}.FACT_APPLICATION
    )MAIN
    LEFT JOIN 
    (
      SELECT 
      A.FACT_PRODUCER_GK,
      A.SRC_ACTIVITY_ID,
      A.ACTIVITY_DATE,
      A.PERSON_GK,
      A.ACTIVITY_TYPE_GK
      FROM ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_job_Target_Schema}.FACT_PRODUCER A, ${v_env_AAW_Database}.${v_job_Target_Schema}.DIM_ACTIVITY_TYPE T
      WHERE A.ACTIVITY_TYPE_GK = T.ACTIVITY_TYPE_GK AND T.ACTIVITY_TYPE_NAME = 'G2' AND A.PERSON_GK > 0
    )LKP
    ON LKP.PERSON_GK = MAIN.APPLICANT_PERSON_GK AND
    LKP.ACTIVITY_DATE >= MAIN.DATE_APPLIED::DATE
  )
) WHERE RN=1
